data.description: Looking for that great opportunity, then look no more. No City Taxes! This home is USDA eligible, which means $0.00 Down Payment if you qualify. This lovely home has lots of natural light and backs up to a green belt. If you are wondering if the hard wood floors are real... the answer is Yes! The bath areas are tiled. The appliances are very clean, almost like new & don't miss the beautiful fireplace. Upstairs is a large loft/game area, large primary bedroom with a spacious closet, tray ceilings & more. Gutters have been installed in the rear of the home & a water softner in the garage. Located near 1604 with easy access to Lackland AFB, HWY 90, Loop 151 & 410. Easy access to Christa Santa Rosa, Baptist Hospital [Under Construction], NW Vista College, and UTSA. There are numerous shopping, eating & entertainment spots such as Sea World, Home Goods, Costco, Olive Garden & many more. Put your creative designs into this home and start creating your new memories. So don't wait, come and see if this ready-to-move in home is the one for you.
